name: Wheel Of Fortune India
description: Recognised by Guinness World Records as the world's most popular TV game show, Wheel of Fortune arrives in India in spectacular fashion, hosted by Akshay Kumar- Contestants enter a thrilling word game, decoding phrases spanning Bollywood, pop culture and everyday life- Blending entertainment with edge-of- the-seat moments, every alphabet can change ttE game as players compete for paisa and prizes-
